    <opTopTitle/>
    <opTopContent>&lt;p&gt;This course helps you understand what Krav Maga is and why is it used for self-defence. By the end of this lesson you will also have basic knowledge on how to defend yourself in basic common attack situations. This lesson is for anyone who is willing to spend sometime to learn basic self-defence, especially women but not limited to women only.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="overview1.gif" width="339" height="360" class="resizable" metadata="obj47" alt="Self defence" style="float: right; border: 0"&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://thegolfclub.info/related/hand-grabbing-neck.html" title="Hand grabbing the neck" target="_blank"&gt;Hand grabbing neck&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href="https://thegolfclub.info/" title="Thegolfclub.info" target="_blank"&gt;Thegolfclub.info&lt;/a&gt; under &lt;a href="http://www.dmlp.org/legal-guide/fair-use" title="Fair Use" target="_blank"&gt;Fair Use&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</opTopContent>
